        <item>
            <title>日本 iPhone 衞星紧急 SOS 启用，无讯号无 Wi-Fi 都可用紧急求救</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/07/30/japaniphone-emergency-sos-via-satellite/software/iphone-app/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=japaniphone-emergency-sos-via-satellite</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/07/30/japaniphone-emergency-sos-via-satellite/software/iphone-app/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Ngan Ivan]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Tue, 30 Jul 2024 14:00:55 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[iPhone app]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[健康]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[智慧城市]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[iPhone 14]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[iPhone 15]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1253708</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p style="font-weight: 400;">Apple 今日宣布将会为日本 iPhone 用户引入通过衞星的紧急求救服务，即使在没有任何手机讯号或网络的情况下依然能使用这项功能。这项功能目前支援安装了 iOS 17.6 或以上版本的 iPhone 14 和 iPhone 15 所有型号，功能自 2022 年推出以来已经为 16 个国家提供服务。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1253719 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/appleemergencysosjpp-414x580.jpg" alt="" width="414" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/appleemergencysosjpp-414x580.jpg 414w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/appleemergencysosjpp.jpg 643w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 414px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1253733" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/appleemergencysosjpp-1-414x580.jpg" alt="" width="414" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/appleemergencysosjpp-1-414x580.jpg 414w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/appleemergencysosjpp-1.jpg 643w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 414px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">图片来源：<a href="https://www.apple.com/jp/newsroom/2024/07/emergency-sos-via-satellite-available-today/">Apple Newsroom</a></p><p style="font-weight: 400;">日本的 iPhone 用户如果遇到紧急情况，但又无法拨打 110、118 或 119（日本紧急求助电话）的时候，只需同时长按侧边按钮和其中一个音量按钮来打开紧急求助 SOS 的滑杆，便可以快速拨打紧急电话。至于衞星紧急 SOS 功能会在用户无法使用讯号或网络求助时，弹出介面容许用户使用衞星紧急 SOS 功能，用户需将 iPhone 指向空中以便与衞星连线并发送资讯。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1253718 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/appleemergencysosjpc-414x580.jpg" alt="" width="414" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/appleemergencysosjpc-414x580.jpg 414w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/appleemergencysosjpc.jpg 643w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 414px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1253720 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/appleemergencysosjpc-1-414x580.jpg" alt="" width="414" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/appleemergencysosjpc-1-414x580.jpg 414w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/appleemergencysosjpc-1.jpg 643w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 414px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">图片来源：<a href="https://www.apple.com/jp/newsroom/2024/07/emergency-sos-via-satellite-available-today/">Apple Newsroom</a></p><p style="font-weight: 400;">用户可以通过衞星紧急 SOS 功能交代自己的情况和地理位置等资讯，这些资讯会被传送至衞星通讯中心的专业人员，发出的短讯大约需要几分钟才会到达。用户在不是危急情况下，但又身处在没有任何手机讯号或网络的地方时，也可以透过衞星的先进技术使用「寻找我的 iPhone」功能来向亲友「报平安」分享自己的地理位置。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1253721 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/appleemergencysosjpf-414x580.jpg" alt="" width="414" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/appleemergencysosjpf-414x580.jpg 414w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/appleemergencysosjpf.jpg 643w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 414px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">图片来源：<a href="https://www.apple.com/jp/newsroom/2024/07/emergency-sos-via-satellite-available-today/">Apple Newsroom</a></p><p style="font-weight: 400;">资料来源：<a href="https://www.apple.com/jp/newsroom/2024/07/emergency-sos-via-satellite-available-today/">Apple Newsroom</a></p><br /><b>相关文章:</b><blockquote><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/07/19/iphone-useful-travel-functions/software/iphone-app/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">【教学】iPhone 用家必学旅游小技巧，教你 Spotlight 查询航班资料、汇率 ＋ 离线地图功能</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/07/12/no-more-sent-from-my-iphone-tutorial/tips-2/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">【教学】令「从我的 iPhone 传送」消失，教你如何制作个人化电子邮件签名</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/07/08/how-to-use-gemini-on-ios-and-android-devices/ai/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">【教学】iPhone 都用到 Gemini　教你如何在 Android 和 iOS 装置上使用</a></li>&nbsp;</blockquote><br /><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/07/30/japaniphone-emergency-sos-via-satellite/software/iphone-app/">日本 iPhone 衞星紧急 SOS 启用，无讯号无 Wi-Fi 都可用紧急求救</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
            </description>
